{"tid":259494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比一間美容中心嘅電話騷擾咗4年 應該點搞","createTime":"2017-05-27T03:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T09:07:35.000Z","uid":111012,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09870b460418fba4336a5a1967a43aa216f507c7","tid":259494,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"第一次借朋友個帳 絲打嚟<br />\n有啲咩得罪嘅唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事源係咁<br />\n自從4年前已經一直收到同一間美容中心嘅電話<br />\n話我之前預約咗上去佢哋荃灣門市做facial 但係我冇到<br />\n佢叫啱我個姓 但係我又冇預約過<br />\n我之前三年一直都係收到就cut 不嬲唔聽廣告電話<br />\n<br />\n點知今日又收到 係未顯示電話號碼 聽咗<br />\n今次終於頂唔順 我話冇預約過 佢話咪玩啦小姐<br />\n我話cancel booking 佢又話冇得cancel 一定要上嚟做一次<br />\n又求晒我又屌我咁 啲語氣躁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我是但話自己未夠18 諗住佢放過我啦（已成年）<br />\n點知佢話等我夠再打過嚟 我心諗使唔使咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底我應該點做 我已經所有2字頭3字頭嘅電話號碼都唔會聽 但係屋企電話打出去係顯示未顯示電話號碼 所以呢啲unknown no.我係一定會接聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左轉電話號碼仲有咩方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個電話號碼對我好有意義 我唔想轉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8665b03f1fc02378a3a6e427246debb871dc9a6e","tid":259494,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:40:27.000Z","msg":"報警？"},{"pid":"0fad194b5ec57bce4df1ac7242eea894cffe4299","tid":259494,"uid":7125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"你下次搵第二個人聽話轉左no. 屌9佢咪撚再煩"},{"pid":"a71a2e21e2121814b21f3d3272ca5cecb4c0423c","tid":259494,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"報警<br />\n<br />\n任何人使用電話傳送令人厭惡、不雅、淫褻、威脅的訊息，或無合理因由不斷打電話，對他人造成煩擾、不便或憂慮，按《簡易程序治罪條例》第20條可處罰款1,000元及監禁兩個月"},{"pid":"889b914e5e07731dd32296b34b7f5e07a3599d6f","tid":259494,"uid":41799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:43:32.000Z","msg":"講咁多做乜鳩，聽左係佢地咪Cut線再Block埋囉，跟手Block埋133搞撚掂"},{"pid":"dffffd24cf36dbf42fd3707a4de9f417623eee3c","tid":259494,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"但係我完全唔知佢係邊間門市<br />\n報警會唔會唔受理 當純粹廣告電話一種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且完全唔明白點解話唔可以cancel Booking<br />\n有冇做呢一行嘅巴打絲打講解吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cde4807a84e6fb5a363e6063e67082f66625a18","tid":259494,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講咁多做乜鳩，聽左係佢地咪Cut線再Block埋囉，跟手Block埋133搞撚掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔得呀兩老成日係屋企會用屋企電話打俾我 但係屋企電話顯示係unknown no. 所以一定唔可以唔聽133<br />\n不過我都唔知點解屋企電話號碼打出去係咁 由細到大都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf0751d067059d5a42073bf84d5d2904f9c3339","tid":259494,"uid":107877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:55:47.000Z","msg":"好明顯昆鳩你上去之後一係比錢一係比人抽插<br />\n同啲咩入境處話你有一封信未攞冇分別<br />\n比我就聽一次屌佢一次再cut線<br />\n咪撚信佢講嘅野"},{"pid":"a73c9cdb9282d4b9d15cd56fc8797c8da6ade0b3","tid":259494,"uid":53911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T03:56:56.000Z","msg":"2字頭3字頭都唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e1d01aa0f091d0b76ddad6d0b689abb886726a","tid":259494,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好明顯昆鳩你上去之後一係比錢一係比人抽插<br />\n同啲咩入境處話你有一封信未攞冇分別<br />\n比我就聽一次屌佢一次再cut線<br />\n咪撚信佢講嘅野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係真係好煩 收電話收到躁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n報警又麻煩又好似冇乜用<br />\n有其他可取方法都唔想報警住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15574c68e6082a7d9be9c5b25d6e62936ca2f2aa","tid":259494,"uid":9607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"Can you speak English?"},{"pid":"38ed0b982ee4a4332d1f90992aacef0eec68548d","tid":259494,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2字頭3字頭都唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該話大部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為通常廣告電話號碼都係35,36開頭 呢啲我就一定唔會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5083d5f133d4754d73ae2bdcf4b17cf0966a6858","tid":259494,"uid":15309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"一打黎就播啲淫叫聲比佢聽<br />\n又或者播啲尖叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8751cf5ea3f691b7c97e2e42ec5c9ba4349f2303","tid":259494,"uid":42900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"一部機用兩張卡，將新電話號碼寫係張紙到，貼係屋企電話隔離，然後block舊號碼133來電。"},{"pid":"9a63527016755096c000a56f149ea36c4bce35a2","tid":259494,"uid":25776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:11:57.000Z","msg":"我都試過 又係比佢氹我叫我上去 比埋whatsapp <br />\n之後我發現係騙局就block哂佢 依家好多 2 字頭3字頭打黎 最勁係一日打成差唔多10次"},{"pid":"87370121bba4455191e53f1331dc80a439793f06","tid":259494,"uid":111012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一打黎就播啲淫叫聲比佢聽<br />\n又或者播啲尖叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj